----------------------------PRIVACY POLICY-------------------------------------------
Welcome to CertifyMe!
Thank you for considering our Google Form Add-on. At CertifyMe, we take privacy seriously and are committed to protecting the personal information of our users.
This privacy policy explains what information we collect through our Google Form Add-on, how we use it, and how we protect it.

Information We Collect 
Our Google Form Add-on uses a minimum amount of scopes, including two default scopes provided by Google and three additional scopes provided by Google Forms Script Editor.
These scopes allow us to access specific data and perform necessary actions within the add-on.
Our Google Form Add-on does not collect any personal information from users. 
We only obtain information from users who have signed up for our services through our company configurations in the Google add-on after installation. 
This information includes:
User Email Address
User Password
User TemplateID

How We Use Information 
We use the information collected from our users solely for the purpose of issuing certificates through the Google Form Add-on. We do not share this information with any third parties or use it for any other purposes.
We may use the email address provided by users to send occasional updates or promotional offers related to our services. Users can opt-out of receiving these emails by contacting us at [info@certifyme.cc].


Data Security 
We take appropriate measures to protect the personal information collected through our Google Form Add-on.
We use industry-standard encryption to ensure that all data is transmitted securely. We also limit access to personal information to authorized personnel who have a legitimate need to access it.

Changes to Privacy Policy 
We reserve the right to update or modify this privacy policy at any time. If we make any significant changes, we will notify users by email or through our website.

Contact Us 
If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy policy or our Google Form Add-on, please contact us at [info@certifyme.cc].
